# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root safety-net ignores for the Varisankya monorepo.
# Each app subdirectory (android/, ios/, web/) keeps its own .gitignore for
# build artifacts; the rules here are an extra guard so NO secret can ever be
# committed from anywhere in the tree, regardless of which directory it lands in.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Credentials / signing material — NEVER commit ──
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
**/serviceAccount*.json
**/play_console_key.json
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks
**/*-upload-key
**/*.p8
**/*.p12
**/*.pem
**/*.cer
**/*.csr
**/*.mobileprovision

# ── Environment files (templates like .env.example stay tracked) ──
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# ── OS / editor / stray artifacts ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/nul
